title: #401 - Steve Simeone
description:
Steve Simeone, Comedian, seen on "This Is Not Happening" on Comedy Central and host of the, "Good Times With: Steve Simeone" podcast. joins Joey Diaz and Lee Syatt live in studio.

Joey and Steve will be performing at the Cherokee Casino in Oklahoma on Saturday, August 6, 2016. Get tickets here:https://goo.gl/qdhezv
